query:
SELECT i.id, p.postUrl, i.status, i.errorMessage, i.interactionType, i.executedAt, i.createdAt 
FROM interactions i 
LEFT JOIN post_urls p ON i.postUrlId = p.id 
WHERE i.interactionType = 'like' 
ORDER BY i.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 5
